OL,3,CWoman arrested after man found dead at
OL,4,CTamworth Railway Station car park
OL,6,FA woman has been arrested after a man
OL,7,Fwas found dead at Tamworth Railway
OL,8,FStation car park.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to Victoria Road
OL,11,Fat around 2.20am on Sunday (March 8th)
OL,12,Ffollowing reports of a man being found
OL,13,Funresponsive.
OL,15,FThe 28-year-old man was treated by
OL,16,Fparamedics but sadly confirmed dead at
OL,17,Fthe scene.
OL,19,FA 28-year-old woman was arrested and
OL,20,Fremains in custody.
