OL,3,CWoman arrested after man found dead at
OL,4,CTamworth Railway Station car park
OL,6,FA scene guard remains in place while
OL,7,Fpolice carry out a forensic
OL,8,Fexamination of the scene. Due to the
OL,9,Flocation, British Transport Police has
OL,10,Fnow taken primacy of the investigation.
OL,12,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Marvin Bruno said:
OL,14,F"Our specialist family liaison
OL,15,Fofficers are providing support to the
OL,16,Fvictim's family and our thoughts
OL,17,Fremain with them at this time.
